OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAngela Rayner pledges fair 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpay talks between workers  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fand bosses                 
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A Labour government would launch "fair 
OL,6, pay agreements" to ensure business and 
OL,7, employees agree and stick by minimum   
OL,8, standards for pay and conditions.      
OL,10,FLabour deputy leader Angela Rayner will
OL,11,Fset out the plan when she opens the    
OL,12,Fparty's conference in Brighton.        
OL,14,FShe will argue that fair pay agreements
OL,15,Fwould "stop bad bosses from exploiting 
OL,16,Ftheir workers and driving down pay".   
OL,18,FIf elected, Labour says it would       
OL,19,Fintroduce the agreements within their  
OL,20,Ffirst 100 days in power.               
